data.title: Voice of Refugees
data.meta_description: "Transforming Lives: Empowering Refugees and Asylum Seekers to Rebuild and Thrive in the United States |Our mission is to put God's love into action, offering comprehensive support and guidance to refugees and asylum seekers, helping them seamlessly reintegrate into American society."
data.text:
For Refugees or Asylum Seekers

If you are a refugee or asylum seeker living in Orange County, we would love to help you!

Please call us at this number: 657-575-0854

CORPORATE PARTNERSHIP

Employment assistance is a critical lifeline for helping refugees and asylum seekers trying to support their families in their first year. Our corporate partners help make this possible.

“There is real fear of not having the right words, or the resources, or the wisdom to serve well, but as I follow God and reach out to others as He has asked us to, I find the joy of Him supplying and growing me in each of those areas.”

– Lisa Mistiuk, volunteer
